{"name":"Troubadour","type":"Item","system":{"description":{"value":"<h2>Troubadour</h2><p>Play the Troubadour if you want to play music to bolster your allies.</p><h3>Spellcast Trait</h3><p>Presence</p><h3>Foundation Feature - Gifted Performer</h3><p>You can play three different types of songs, once each per long rest:</p><ul><li><strong>Relaxing Song:</strong> You and all allies within Close range clear a Hit Point.</li><li><strong>Epic Song:</strong> Make a target within Close range temporarily Vulnerable.</li><li><strong>Heartbreaking Song:</strong> You and all allies within Close range gain a Hope.</li></ul>"},"parentClass":"bard","spellcastTrait":"presence"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_id":"troubadour000000001"}
